538
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,880
Mother, you and I are different.

539
00:33:53,080 --> 00:33:56,360
I rather spend my life with my loved one.

540
00:33:56,560 --> 00:33:58,720
I am not as ambitious as Mother.

541
00:33:59,040 --> 00:34:01,560
I cannot give up my love in exchange of power.

542
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:04,120
Please forgive me that I can't obey this order.

543
00:34:04,320 --> 00:34:06,040
Do you know what you're saying?

544
00:34:06,360 --> 00:34:07,600
I'm your Mother.

545
00:34:07,840 --> 00:34:09,639
Mother, would you rather see me as an Emperor...

546
00:34:10,080 --> 00:34:12,000
than a person with happiness?

547
00:34:12,639 --> 00:34:14,560
What you told me today...

548
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:16,560
I will forget it,

549
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:19,000
and will not say a single word to anyone.

550
00:34:19,280 --> 00:34:20,639
Mother, please forget today's conversation as well.

551
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:22,280
I need to deal with some military affairs.

552
00:34:22,800 --> 00:34:23,760
I will take a leave now.

553
00:34:24,760 --> 00:34:27,239
You have to keep every single word in mind.

554
00:34:27,520 --> 00:34:30,800
One day, you will understand why I said these.

555
00:34:31,040 --> 00:34:34,600
The world is not as easy as you think.

556
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:37,679
I don't know when you will be clear-headed.

557
00:34:37,880 --> 00:34:39,719
But now,

558
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:42,080
getting married to Sui He is your only option!

559
00:34:53,199 --> 00:34:54,639
Sui He.

560
00:34:55,360 --> 00:34:57,360
Don't blame on Xu Feng.

561
00:35:00,720 --> 00:35:03,240
His Highness will understand you one day.

562
00:35:05,600 --> 00:35:07,800
Why will I blame on him?

563
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:11,160
If I need to blame on someone,

564
00:35:11,680 --> 00:35:13,960
that person will be Jin Mi.

565
00:35:14,520 --> 00:35:16,600
She bewitched His Highness's heart.

566
00:35:17,280 --> 00:35:21,280
I'm surprised that Jin Mi is your daughter.

567
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:22,560
I'm surprised...

568
00:35:22,800 --> 00:35:24,120
Your Majesty once thought that

569
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,480
Jin Mi is the daughter of you and Zi Fen.

570
00:35:26,600 --> 00:35:27,400
Luo Lin.

571
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:29,880
What have you discovered?

572
00:35:30,040 --> 00:35:32,680
I have discovered everything I need to know.

573
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:33,360
Luo Lin.

574
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:38,560
Zi Fen was my true love.

575
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:42,480
You said Zi Fen was your true love...

576
00:35:43,200 --> 00:35:45,440
Then why would you hurt her body...

577
00:35:45,720 --> 00:35:47,080
and break her heart?

578
00:35:47,800 --> 00:35:48,920
I know.

579
00:35:49,520 --> 00:35:51,000
It's all my fault.

580
00:35:51,400 --> 00:35:53,560
I was being jealous and stunned.

581
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:55,440
I arranged the marriage of you and Lin Xiu...

582
00:35:55,640 --> 00:35:57,200
was to keep Zi Fen by my side.

583
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:58,640
But I never knew...

584
00:35:58,760 --> 00:36:00,840
she still left with regrets.

585
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:07,240
Do you know the reason behind Zi Fen's death?

586
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:09,960
According to Floral Realm's announcement,

587
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:12,600
after Zi Fen went back,

588
00:36:13,720 --> 00:36:15,280
she was unhappy all day long,

589
00:36:16,080 --> 00:36:20,040
and at the end... died with a grievance.

590
00:36:20,560 --> 00:36:21,880
Zi Fen.

591
00:36:22,120 --> 00:36:24,520
Do you really not want me to tell him?

592
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:29,480
You know Floral Realm and I are willing to die for you.

593
00:36:33,680 --> 00:36:37,680
I'm willing to bear all the charges.

594
00:36:37,760 --> 00:36:38,960
Bear?

595
00:36:39,280 --> 00:36:41,440
Zi Fen is dead.

596
00:36:42,120 --> 00:36:43,840
My daughter,

597
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,320
in these 4000 years,

598
00:36:46,560 --> 00:36:49,240
never saw her mother once!

599
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:51,560
How would you possible to bear it?

600
00:36:54,520 --> 00:36:55,440
I understand.

601
00:36:56,960 --> 00:36:58,600
In these 4000 years,

602
00:37:00,600 --> 00:37:02,120
every time I think of this,

603
00:37:04,760 --> 00:37:06,780
I cannot forgive myself.

604
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,560
Luo Lin.

605
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,280
I'm now...

606
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:16,680
I'm now begging you, as a friend,

607
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:20,760
I hope you and Zi Fen can forgive me.

608
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:23,720
I have lost Zi Fen...

609
00:37:26,240 --> 00:37:28,360
I can't bear to lost my best friend as well.

610
00:37:32,160 --> 00:37:34,280
I will not forgive you.

611
00:37:36,080 --> 00:37:37,320
Otherwise,

612
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:41,680
I can't face Zi Fen.

613
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:45,000
What I can do now

614
00:37:45,200 --> 00:37:47,440
is too follow Zi Fen's will.

615
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:50,640
An eye for an eye makes the whole world go blind.

616
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:55,840
To make the world stay peaceful,

617
00:37:57,520 --> 00:38:01,760
Zi Fen... would be the only one to be sacrificed.

618
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:03,680
I know.

619
00:38:05,600 --> 00:38:07,960
Jin Mi is the daughter of you and Zi Fen.

620
00:38:08,640 --> 00:38:10,360
When she gets married to Run Yu,

621
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,600
she will be my daughter-in-law.

622
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,040
By then,

623
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:18,960
I will host...

624
00:38:19,280 --> 00:38:21,680
the biggest wedding ceremony for them.

625
00:38:22,160 --> 00:38:23,440
As a...

626
00:38:24,400 --> 00:38:28,320
a little payback to you and Zi Fen.

627
00:38:31,520 --> 00:38:34,240
If Jin Mi is not fond of Run Yu,

628
00:38:35,240 --> 00:38:40,680
I will never allow my daughter to have any connection...

629
00:38:40,680 --> 00:38:44,680
to Heaven Realm.

630
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:50,160
You are so respected in Heaven Realm.

631
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:53,120
I can't allow you to have any resentment to me.

632
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:55,680
But, to Jin Mi,

633
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:58,240
I will treat her well sincerely.


